project_description: Pre-packaged, pre-configured JupyterLab environment with NVIDIA GPU support, curated data science packages, TensorFlow, PyTorch, and integrated services (MLFlow, TensorBoard, Glances) running behind Traefik reverse proxy
version_comment: Major refactoring of lab utilities with improved UX - renamed workspace-utils to lab-utils, grouped git operations under git-utils menu, renamed install-code-assistant to install-ai-assistant, added JupyterLab launcher tile with proper terminal initialization wrapper, added jupyterlab_parquet_viewer_extension and jupyterlab_mmd_to_png_extension for enhanced data visualization and mermaid diagram export capabilities, updated all documentation and screenshots to reflect new naming conventions
